name: Backrooms: The Travelers Guide
description:
Hey! If you're looking for an older build, they're probably gonna be uploaded here!

Long story short, I ended up in The Backrooms. Well... I don't think we can leave, so I guess you're stuck with me now! Yay!

Minimum Specs:

  • Windows 10 (64-bit)
  • Quad-core Intel or AMD processor, 1.6 GHz or faster.
  • NVIDIA GeForce 470 GTX or AMD Radeon 6870 HD series card or higher.
  • 4 GB RAM or more.
  • At least 256MB of Storage.
